00:00:42,167 --> 00:00:45,962
LIKE FLOWERS IN SAND

2
00:00:47,130 --> 00:00:50,675
Ayah ada latihan. Jangan lupa sarapan.

3
00:01:17,452 --> 00:01:22,582
Semasa kecil, orang selalu beritahu saya,

4
00:01:23,792 --> 00:01:26,169
"Tentu awak sunyi, Du-sik.

5
00:01:26,252 --> 00:01:28,755
Tentu awak bosan di rumah seorang diri."

6
00:01:31,591 --> 00:01:35,553
Tapi mereka tak tahu hakikatnya.

7
00:01:37,347 --> 00:01:41,518
Saya tak pernah rasa sunyi atau bosan.

8
00:01:46,272 --> 00:01:47,816
- Sakitlah! 
- Pertama,

9
00:01:47,899 --> 00:01:50,151
saya ada Kim Baek-du yang selalu

10
00:01:50,235 --> 00:01:52,070
- Tunggu! 
- menemani saya.

11
00:01:52,153 --> 00:01:53,613
Hei, Oh Du-sik!

12
00:01:53,696 --> 00:01:55,073
- Belum sikat… 
- Tak apa.

13
00:01:55,156 --> 00:01:56,658
Tunggu. Makan ini dulu.

14
00:01:56,741 --> 00:01:57,784
- Dah. 
- Satu lagi.

15
00:01:57,867 --> 00:01:59,119
Saya juga ada Jin-su.

16
00:01:59,202 --> 00:02:01,496
- Hei, Baek-du. 
- Jin-su!

17
00:02:01,579 --> 00:02:04,290
Hai, anak-anak.

18
00:02:04,374 --> 00:02:07,836
Jangan lupa buku nota kamu. 
Kerja rumah dah siap?

19
00:02:07,919 --> 00:02:09,838
- Saya pergi dulu. 
- Pegang ini.

20
00:02:09,921 --> 00:02:11,589
Kunyah betul-betul.

21
00:02:11,673 --> 00:02:14,217
Kalau dah jatuh, jangan kutip.

22
00:02:14,300 --> 00:02:16,219
- Okey. 
- Tunggu!

23
00:02:16,302 --> 00:02:18,054
Jangan bergaduh atau melahu!

24
00:02:19,389 --> 00:02:20,723
Awak macam budak lelaki.

25
00:02:20,807 --> 00:02:21,724
Awak lelaki.

26
00:02:23,935 --> 00:02:25,937
- Seok-hui juga. 
- Kerja rumah siap?

27
00:02:26,020 --> 00:02:27,188
Awak lupa?

28
00:02:27,272 --> 00:02:30,150
Kerja rumah senang saja. 
Saya jawab banyak soalan.

29
00:02:33,945 --> 00:02:34,904
Apa jawapannya?

30
00:02:35,530 --> 00:02:36,739
Satu.

31
00:02:36,823 --> 00:02:38,533
- Saya dah macam nenek. 
- Salah!

32
00:02:39,951 --> 00:02:41,786
Mi-ran juga ada.

33
00:02:47,584 --> 00:02:48,501
Mi-ran!

34
00:02:51,254 --> 00:02:54,883
Kami semua sentiasa bersama.

35
00:03:00,680 --> 00:03:06,519
EPISOD 10 
IKATAN YANG TIADA PENGAKHIRAN

36
00:03:08,271 --> 00:03:09,814
Saya suka awak.

37
00:03:11,733 --> 00:03:13,151
Saya betul-betul suka awak.

38
00:03:17,488 --> 00:03:19,824
Jadi…

39
00:03:20,575 --> 00:03:23,995
maksud awak,

40
00:03:25,163 --> 00:03:26,414
awak ada hati…

41
00:03:27,332 --> 00:03:29,000
- pada saya? 
- Ya.

42
00:03:29,083 --> 00:03:30,752
- Saya suka awak. 
- Okey.

43
00:03:30,835 --> 00:03:32,545
Jangan ulang lagi.

44
00:03:33,421 --> 00:03:34,923
Saya faham.

45
00:03:37,634 --> 00:03:38,468
Okey.

46
00:03:39,552 --> 00:03:40,762
Sebenarnya,

47
00:03:41,846 --> 00:03:44,182
saya betul-betul tak sangka.

48
00:03:45,725 --> 00:03:48,603
Awak memang selalu

49
00:03:49,270 --> 00:03:51,981
buat saya bingung.

50
00:03:52,482 --> 00:03:53,399
Betul.

51
00:03:53,983 --> 00:03:55,902
Apabila saya sedar saya suka awak,

52
00:03:55,985 --> 00:03:57,612
- saya juga… 
- Cukup!

53
00:03:59,697 --> 00:04:03,201
Jangan cakap awak suka saya lagi.

54
00:04:04,619 --> 00:04:07,163
Janggal rasanya.

55
00:04:12,627 --> 00:04:16,714
Kenapa awak pandang saya begitu?

56
00:04:26,391 --> 00:04:27,350
Hei.

57
00:04:28,851 --> 00:04:29,686
Kim Baek-du.

58
00:04:32,689 --> 00:04:34,899
- Saya… 
- Jangan!

59
00:04:35,984 --> 00:04:38,194
Saya tak nak dengar jawapan awak dulu.

60
00:04:39,612 --> 00:04:40,947
Awak tak nak dengar?

61
00:04:42,073 --> 00:04:44,575
Jadi kenapa awak beritahu saya?

62
00:04:44,659 --> 00:04:47,537
Macam yang saya cakap tadi,

63
00:04:47,620 --> 00:04:49,580
saya tak mahu menyesal lagi.

64
00:04:50,415 --> 00:04:52,125
Kalau saya tak buat apa-apa

65
00:04:52,625 --> 00:04:55,086
dan biarkan awak pulang ke Seoul,

66
00:04:55,670 --> 00:04:57,380
kali ini,

67
00:04:57,463 --> 00:05:01,092
saya akan menyesal selama 200 tahun, 
bukan 20 tahun saja!

68
00:05:02,719 --> 00:05:05,722
Jadi biar saya tolong awak.

69
00:05:06,306 --> 00:05:07,140
Tidak.

70
00:05:08,433 --> 00:05:09,726
Saya akan tolong awak.

71
00:05:16,316 --> 00:05:18,818
Baek-du, budak bertuah itu

72
00:05:19,861 --> 00:05:22,405
buat jantung saya rasa macam nak pecah.

73
00:05:22,488 --> 00:05:23,698
MINUM SAMPAI MABUK!

74
00:05:24,449 --> 00:05:26,617
Hati awak yang akan pecah dulu.

75
00:05:31,122 --> 00:05:34,000
Awak akan menyesal esok.

76
00:05:34,083 --> 00:05:36,127
Apabila awak bangun pagi esok…

77
00:05:37,378 --> 00:05:38,629
Aduhai.

78
00:05:41,174 --> 00:05:42,425
Hyeon-ja.

79
00:05:42,967 --> 00:05:45,011
Awak pernah teringatkan Du-sik?

80
00:05:46,596 --> 00:05:48,598
Mestilah pernah.

81
00:05:50,183 --> 00:05:55,521
Budak-budak itu selalu main sama-sama.

82
00:05:56,105 --> 00:05:58,441
Kadang-kadang saya teringatkan dia.

83
00:05:59,108 --> 00:06:01,360
Saya terfikir di mana agaknya dia,

84
00:06:01,444 --> 00:06:04,280
apa khabar dia,

85
00:06:04,363 --> 00:06:06,032
dia dah kahwin atau belum?

86
00:06:07,116 --> 00:06:08,576
Awak pula?

87
00:06:10,995 --> 00:06:12,789
Ada sesuatu yang selalu

88
00:06:13,831 --> 00:06:15,249
mengganggu fikiran saya.

89
00:06:18,753 --> 00:06:20,421
Du-sik

90
00:06:21,380 --> 00:06:24,717
sebaya dengan Baek-du, 
tapi dia lebih pintar.

91
00:06:25,343 --> 00:06:28,596
Nampak kasar di luar, 
tapi lembut di dalam.

92
00:06:28,679 --> 00:06:29,931
Ya.

93
00:06:32,141 --> 00:06:33,684
Tentu dia

94
00:06:35,019 --> 00:06:37,396
sangat terluka ketika itu.

95
00:06:44,153 --> 00:06:45,113
Sudahlah.

96
00:06:45,196 --> 00:06:47,824
- Saya nak minum. 
- Biar saya tuangkan.

97
00:06:51,202 --> 00:06:52,912
Kita minum sama-sama.

98
00:06:59,669 --> 00:07:01,587
Tapi manusia sentiasa berubah.

99
00:07:02,171 --> 00:07:04,549
Dulu saya teringatkan dia 100 kali sehari.

100
00:07:05,091 --> 00:07:08,094
Lama-kelamaan, 
berkurang ke 50 kali sehari.

101
00:07:09,220 --> 00:07:12,682
Selepas itu, 
lebih kurang sepuluh kali sehari.

102
00:07:14,308 --> 00:07:15,601
Kadang-kadang,

103
00:07:16,269 --> 00:07:19,105
saya langsung tak teringatkan dia.

104
00:07:19,939 --> 00:07:24,068
Saya faham. Kerana ia sudah lama berlalu.

105
00:07:26,070 --> 00:07:27,572
Anak saya, Baek-du…

106
00:07:28,990 --> 00:07:32,034
Apa? Aduhai.

107
00:07:32,118 --> 00:07:33,661
Dulu,

108
00:07:34,620 --> 00:07:37,039
selepas Du-sik pergi,

109
00:07:40,001 --> 00:07:43,421
berhari-hari dia menangis.

110
00:07:43,963 --> 00:07:46,466
Kemudian dia nampak okey,

111
00:07:47,300 --> 00:07:52,138
jadi saya sangka dia dah lupakan Du-sik. 
Mungkin dia lupa kerana dia masih kecil.

112
00:07:52,680 --> 00:07:55,892
Tak sangka betul.

113
00:08:02,064 --> 00:08:04,358
Saya ibunya,

114
00:08:06,903 --> 00:08:10,364
tapi saya tak tahu 
apa yang anak saya lalui.

115
00:08:11,282 --> 00:08:12,867
Saya langsung tak tahu.

116
00:08:13,951 --> 00:08:16,579
Saya ibu paling teruk di dunia.

117
00:08:19,749 --> 00:08:21,667
Saya…

118
00:08:22,668 --> 00:08:25,213
- Jin-suk. 
- Sakit kepala saya.

119
00:08:25,296 --> 00:08:27,298
Awak dah mabuk.

120
00:08:29,717 --> 00:08:32,553
Lebih baik saya mati saja.

121
00:08:32,637 --> 00:08:35,181
- Jangan cakap begitu. 
- Aduhai.

122
00:08:35,973 --> 00:08:39,685
Apa gunanya saya hidup?

123
00:08:39,769 --> 00:08:40,686
Aduhai.

124
00:08:40,770 --> 00:08:42,063
- Yalah. 
- Betul tak?

125
00:08:42,146 --> 00:08:43,356
Jangan minum lagi.

126
00:08:43,439 --> 00:08:44,273
Suk.

127
00:08:46,150 --> 00:08:48,653
Aduhai. Helo.

128
00:08:49,946 --> 00:08:51,239
- Jin-suk. 
- Nanti.

129
00:08:52,698 --> 00:08:55,368
Saya kenal lelaki ini.

130
00:08:55,451 --> 00:08:58,037
Kenapa awak minum banyak sangat?

131
00:08:58,746 --> 00:09:00,831
Saya macam kenal lelaki ini.

132
00:09:01,874 --> 00:09:03,376
Mana saya pernah jumpa dia?

133
00:09:03,876 --> 00:09:06,337
- Aduhai. 
- Saya mabuk.

134
00:09:06,420 --> 00:09:09,590
Dia bukan apa.

135
00:09:09,674 --> 00:09:11,842
Dia cuma sedih sikit hari ini.

136
00:09:11,926 --> 00:09:13,553
Jin-suk.

137
00:09:14,971 --> 00:09:16,806
Sebenarnya…

138
00:09:16,889 --> 00:09:19,642
Di depan semua orang, Baek-du cakap…

139
00:09:19,725 --> 00:09:21,394
- Du-sik… 
- Saya ada dengar

140
00:09:21,477 --> 00:09:22,478
sebelum ke sini.

141
00:09:22,562 --> 00:09:24,063
Okey.

142
00:09:25,606 --> 00:09:28,276
Di mata orang lain,

143
00:09:28,359 --> 00:09:31,112
mungkin Baek-du cuma nampak marah,

144
00:09:31,195 --> 00:09:34,240
tapi ibu dia boleh nampak

145
00:09:34,323 --> 00:09:36,867
betapa hancurnya hati dia.

146
00:09:42,915 --> 00:09:44,208
Hei.

147
00:09:44,834 --> 00:09:46,961
Kim Tae-baek.

148
00:09:50,756 --> 00:09:51,799
Apa?

149
00:09:57,722 --> 00:09:58,639
Apa?

150
00:10:00,600 --> 00:10:04,186
Orang tua macam kita…

151
00:10:06,230 --> 00:10:08,608
dah banyak buat salah.

152
00:10:10,067 --> 00:10:11,319
Betul tak?

153
00:10:15,156 --> 00:10:16,032
Ya.

154
00:10:18,075 --> 00:10:20,161
Orang tua banyak buat salah.

155
00:10:27,126 --> 00:10:30,588
Penatnya.

156
00:11:06,248 --> 00:11:07,333
Ada apa, ayah?

157
00:11:10,670 --> 00:11:11,712
Kamu belum tidur?

158
00:11:16,592 --> 00:11:17,843
Ayah dah tahu semuanya.

159
00:11:21,931 --> 00:11:23,766
Yakah?

160
00:11:26,727 --> 00:11:30,398
Nampaknya cerita dah tersebar.

161
00:11:32,358 --> 00:11:33,818
Cepat betul.

162
00:11:36,195 --> 00:11:38,364
Sebab itu kamu cakap begitu?

163
00:11:40,199 --> 00:11:41,033
Apa?

164
00:11:43,119 --> 00:11:46,414
Kamu kata kita tak patut 
biarkan Du-sik pergi

165
00:11:48,582 --> 00:11:52,586
dan cuba sedaya upaya untuk bantu dia 
supaya dia tak perlu pindah.

166
00:11:54,797 --> 00:11:56,841
Itu…

167
00:11:59,468 --> 00:12:00,428
Baek-du.

168
00:12:02,430 --> 00:12:03,347
Dulu,

169
00:12:04,348 --> 00:12:05,933
ayah tiada pilihan.

170
00:12:07,685 --> 00:12:08,853
Dalam hidup ini,

171
00:12:09,854 --> 00:12:12,857
ada ketikanya, kita perlu buat keputusan.

172
00:12:13,357 --> 00:12:17,611
Ayah tak selalunya 
buat keputusan yang betul.

173
00:12:19,613 --> 00:12:21,699
Ayah cuma cuba mencari jawapan terbaik

174
00:12:23,451 --> 00:12:25,828
dalam situasi tertentu.

175
00:12:29,081 --> 00:12:30,166
Dan ketika itu,

176
00:12:32,126 --> 00:12:33,752
itu pilihan terbaik bagi ayah.

177
00:12:38,215 --> 00:12:40,009
Tapi hari ini, ayah sedar

178
00:12:42,136 --> 00:12:43,929
mungkin itu bukan jawapannya.

179
00:13:00,404 --> 00:13:01,989
Saya suka awak.

180
00:13:03,532 --> 00:13:06,160
Saya betul-betul suka awak.

181
00:13:07,536 --> 00:13:11,040
Awak tahu berapa kali saya terkenang

182
00:13:11,749 --> 00:13:13,125
dan menyesali malam itu?

183
00:13:14,293 --> 00:13:15,711
"Saya sepatutnya lari lebih laju.

184
00:13:16,879 --> 00:13:18,756
Saya sepatutnya jerit lebih kuat.

185
00:13:18,839 --> 00:13:20,799
Saya sepatutnya keluar lebih awal."

186
00:13:21,342 --> 00:13:24,011
Tidak. "Saya sepatutnya boleh agak

187
00:13:24,595 --> 00:13:28,516
ketika awak datang ke rumah saya."

188
00:13:30,059 --> 00:13:32,520
Saya menyesalinya beratus ribu kali.

189
00:13:33,646 --> 00:13:35,439
Tapi saya tak mahu menyesal lagi.

190
00:13:38,317 --> 00:13:40,778
Saya masih kecil ketika itu.

191
00:13:41,946 --> 00:13:45,199
Saya tak mampu halang 
dan terpaksa lepaskan awak.

192
00:13:45,282 --> 00:13:46,867
Tapi bukan kali ini.

193
00:13:53,916 --> 00:13:55,668
Jadi biar saya tolong awak.

194
00:13:56,168 --> 00:13:58,921
Tidak. Saya akan tolong awak.

195
00:14:18,691 --> 00:14:20,109
Hei!

196
00:14:21,110 --> 00:14:23,404
Terkejut ibu!

197
00:14:24,071 --> 00:14:26,282
Kenapa kamu berdiri di situ?

198
00:14:26,365 --> 00:14:29,368
Ibu sangka ibu kena culik.

199
00:14:30,369 --> 00:14:32,204
Aduh, sakitnya kepala ibu.

200
00:14:33,414 --> 00:14:37,126
Kepala ibu rasa macam nak pecah.

201
00:14:37,209 --> 00:14:39,295
Saya dengar ibu minum banyak semalam.

202
00:14:39,378 --> 00:14:40,212
Minum di mana?

203
00:14:42,256 --> 00:14:44,466
Di mana lagi? Restoran Jin-sulah.

204
00:14:44,550 --> 00:14:46,510
Saya dah cakap.

205
00:14:50,431 --> 00:14:52,266
Aduh, sakitnya kepala.

206
00:14:52,892 --> 00:14:55,811
Pukul berapa ibu balik malam tadi?

207
00:14:59,231 --> 00:15:00,941
Hyeon-ja hantar ibu balik?

208
00:15:01,025 --> 00:15:02,651
Dari dulu lagi saya rasa

209
00:15:02,735 --> 00:15:05,946
ibu tak ada hak nak membebel 
setiap kali Baek-du mabuk.

210
00:15:06,030 --> 00:15:07,615
Dia ikut perangai ibu.

211
00:15:07,698 --> 00:15:09,408
Hei, tepi.

212
00:15:09,491 --> 00:15:11,452
Tepilah.

213
00:15:12,244 --> 00:15:15,164
Ibu tak patut marah-marah 
Baek-du kalau dia minum.

214
00:15:15,247 --> 00:15:16,540
Aduh, sakitnya.

215
00:15:17,666 --> 00:15:19,627
Kenapa? Ada apa-apa berlaku semalam?

216
00:15:19,710 --> 00:15:21,962
Ayah dukung ibu balik semalam.

217
00:15:22,046 --> 00:15:23,797
Dia bubuh koyok di badannya.

218
00:15:23,881 --> 00:15:26,383
- Ya. 
- Dia bubuh banyak di belakangnya

219
00:15:26,467 --> 00:15:29,511
sampai nampak macam jubin lantai bersusun.

220
00:15:29,595 --> 00:15:30,846
Ya.

221
00:15:32,389 --> 00:15:35,726
Ibu nak tahu tak? 
Kami pergi joging pagi tadi

222
00:15:35,809 --> 00:15:38,437
dan kami dengar cerita kurang enak.

223
00:15:38,520 --> 00:15:42,650
Kami dengar Baek-du cakap tentang Du-sik 
di depan orang kampung

224
00:15:42,733 --> 00:15:45,235
dan mengamuk semalam. Betulkah?

225
00:15:52,576 --> 00:15:53,494
Mana Baek-du?

226
00:15:54,119 --> 00:15:55,496
Dia keluar pagi tadi.

227
00:15:55,579 --> 00:15:57,206
Tentu dia malu.

228
00:15:57,289 --> 00:16:00,167
Semua orang bercakap tentang dia.

229
00:16:03,003 --> 00:16:05,798
Aduhai. Biar saya lihat.

230
00:16:05,881 --> 00:16:09,718
Awak tahu tak Baek-du mengamuk semalam?

231
00:16:09,802 --> 00:16:11,553
Tak mungkin.

232
00:16:11,637 --> 00:16:13,639
Saya tak pernah nampak dia marah.

233
00:16:13,722 --> 00:16:15,182
Saya pun tak pernah.

234
00:16:15,265 --> 00:16:18,435
Katanya kita tak percaya 
keluarga Du-sik dan usir mereka.

235
00:16:18,519 --> 00:16:19,770
Dia betul-betul marah.

236
00:16:19,853 --> 00:16:22,314
- Apa? Betulkah? 
- Ya.

237
00:16:22,398 --> 00:16:24,525
Kenapa tiba-tiba ungkit soal Du-sik?

238
00:16:24,608 --> 00:16:26,860
Entahlah. Mak dia tanya

239
00:16:26,944 --> 00:16:29,947
sama ada betul dia bercinta 
dengan si Yu-gyeong itu,

240
00:16:30,030 --> 00:16:32,324
kemudian dia tiba-tiba naik darah.

241
00:16:32,825 --> 00:16:34,284
- Yakah? 
- Ya.

242
00:16:35,536 --> 00:16:37,121
Tak macam Baek-du langsung.

243
00:16:37,204 --> 00:16:38,747
- Ya. 
- Dia budak baik.

244
00:16:38,831 --> 00:16:41,041
- Betul. 
- Aduhai.

245
00:16:51,969 --> 00:16:54,513
